    "Prompt developmentThe design of this study is structured around comparing performance of two popular chatbots, ChatGPT and Bing Chat, in evaluating the veracity of statements related to different socio-political topics.",
    "We particularly focus on the differences in settings and guardrails in place regarding different socially relevant political topics.",
